  "texts": [
    "Fundus examination revealed right optic disc swelling.",
    "Her past medical history was notable for well-controlled hypertension, uterine fibroids, and benign glomus tympanicum tumor that was fully resected.",
    "She worked from home in human resources and did not use tobacco or drugs or drink alcohol.",
    "Family history was noncontributory.",
    "A month prior to the onset of symptoms, she had received the Pfizer COVID-19 booster shot and an influenza vaccine."
  ]
}